title: Smart Designer X3
description:
This is a really great add on for Corel Draw X3 (will not work with X4). Not only does it simplify a lot of things in Corel Draw it has a lot of extra features. For Embroiders/Screen Printers that need to do a split front it automatically creates it for you. A lot of features for screen printers. Actually anyone that uses Corel Draw with find usefull tools. It also includes a customer manager and pricing manager. Not to mention it comes with dozens of templates and to change text it is very easy.

The only drawback is that this is a 30 day trial without using a valid serial number that is created using the machine ID code. So hopefully someone will find a crack or a key generator for this program.
